CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 16, 1952, pg. 10 reads: "Debs Dance - Six cute little sub-debs entertained about twenty of their friends at a dinner dance held last Friday at the Greene Hearth. Pictured with their sponsor(s), Miss Sylvia Calloway, are, left to right, Roberta Ratcliff, Nancy Jones, Sylvia King, Luella Blow, Wilma Johnson and Barbara Flood. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Debutants, left to right: Roberta Ratcliff, Nancy Jones, Sylvia King, sponsor Sylvia Calloway, Luella Blow, Wilma Johnson and Barbara Flood, posed around table in the Greene Hearth restaurant
